  "texts": [
    "Finally, the authors evaluated R2D2 in the 57 games of ALE and the different tasks of the DMLab-30 environment.",
    "They compared their results with those obtained by Ape-X (Horgan et al. 2018) and IMPALA (Espeholt et al. 2018).",
    "Unlike R2D2, the hyperparameters were adjusted separately for each environment.",
    "The authors pointed out that one of the most significant contributions of DQN was its ability to generalize over different environments using the same network architecture and hyperparameter values.",
    "According to them, until the date of their publication, no other work had maintained this kind of generalization pattern, using the same architecture and hyperparameters in both the ALE and DMLab-30 environments."
  ],
